document_data.mainbody:
Mraedaras Street was a road that crossed the entirety of The Shutters neighborhood in the Crows End District of Ravens Bluff from north to south, and ended in the Pumpside neighborhood.
Mraedaras Street was only three city blocks in length. It began at Karen Court in The Shutters in the north, and moved straight south, crossing Hammerstone Street, Drovers Run, and ended on Conant Court.
* Fellowship of Exalted Adventurers, a young boys club formed in the late 14 century DR.
